        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="CH1a0902-start">
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-13a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T16:02:59.741+09:00">I question this, saying:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-13a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T16:10:54.58+09:00">Mozi wants one not to wear mourning robes when a relative dies</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-13a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T17:43:22.058+09:00">Because [he wants one] to find peace on one's own accord and to completely conduct the mourning oneself,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-13a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T18:05:27.071+09:00">In vain he takes Yanzi as a source of authority,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-13a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T18:05:29.661+09:00">adapts [Yanzi's position] to his own,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-13a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T18:07:19.642+09:00">coincidentally proving that he his wrong.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-13a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T19:13:48.609+09:00">Besides, Yanzi mourned his father in accordance with the rites and so did not follow</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-13a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T19:14:40.979+09:00">those that oppose the conduction of the rites.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-12a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T19:15:13.675+09:00">Mozi said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-12a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T19:56:45.477+09:00">"When Duke Jing ascended to the Great Chamber,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-12a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T19:57:36.496+09:00">he heard the sound of wailing.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-12a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T19:58:44.341+09:00">He asked Liang Qiuju about it and</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-12a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T19:58:50.831+09:00">he answered:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-12a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:01:04.025+09:00">He is a follower of Confucius from Lu.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-12a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:01:06.907+09:00">His mother died,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-12a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:01:43.73+09:00">he will wear mourning robes for three years,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-12a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:04:13.781+09:00">and wail and cry in extreme grief."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-12a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:04:10.701+09:00">The Duke said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-12a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:05:29.493+09:00">"Isn't this impossible?!"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-12a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:05:40.494+09:00">Yanzi said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-12a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:15:14.395+09:00">"The sages of old, it is not that they were not capable of this,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-12a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:09:07.107+09:00">but they would not do it,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-12a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:17:42.558+09:00">for they knew that they had nothing to replace the dead person,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-12a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:14:45.233+09:00">but deeply harm the affairs of the living."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-14a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:26:45.855+09:00">Cao Ming asked Ziyu:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-14a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:25:19.045+09:00">"I have read your objections against the Mohists,  </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-13a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:22:39.743+09:00">and wail for three days only.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-14a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:29:26.018+09:00">the opposite is the case,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-14a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:29:38.087+09:00">the Mohists are lying.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-14a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:31:18.33+09:00">If the Mohists were to rise again,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-14a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:32:31.88+09:00">could you fend them off?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-14a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:32:48.893+09:00">Ziyu answered:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-14a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:47:28.759+09:00">"As long as one knows their principles (理),</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-14a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:52:51.999+09:00">on will make a clear case even against hundreds of Mohists.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-14a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:53:57.294+09:00">Once one loses track of their standards,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-14a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:54:55.055+09:00">one will not be able to confront a single man.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0902_CHANT_006-14a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#crone.thomas" modified="2020-11-18T20:55:41.569+09:00">What Mozi </seg>
                </p>
            </div>
